toolbox.name: PostDeepLearning
toolbox.alias: Toolbox for post-processing deep learning results

dataIdInfo.idPurp: The Post Deep Learning Workflows geoprocessing tool contains two main tools for post-processing deep learning results: PostDeepLearningBuildingsWorkflows and PostDeepLearningRoadsWorkflows. Below is a summary of each tool

Parameter.Name: Input Raster
Parameter.Description: The raster dataset to be processed.

Parameter.Name: Field Name for Raster to Polygon
Parameter.Description: The field name used for converting raster to polygon.

Parameter.Name: Unique Value of Selected Field
Parameter.Description: The unique value in the specified field to retain.

Parameter.Name: Output Feature Class
Parameter.Description: The output feature class for the processed features.
